Class Location

java.lang.Object
  JsonableModel
      in.ubee.api.models.Location

public class Location
extends JsonableModel

A point representing it's absolute position (x, y) to a image. This point is the result of the indoor location positioning system in a Retail. Its coordinates (x , y) is relative to a Retail Map Image. Its floor is the Retail Map floor;

Location

public Location(float x,
                float y,
                int floor,
                double precision,
                java.lang.String retailId)
A point representing it's relative position (x, y) to a image. Also has the floor of the Retail's Map and the precision of the point This point is the result of the indoor location positioning system. Its coordinates (x , y) is relative to the Retail Map Image.

Parameters:
x - the x relative position in the Retail Map Image
y - the y relative position in the Retail Map Image
floor - the floor of the Retail Map
precision - precision in percentage of the position
retailId - the retail id of the position
